<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<ScrollView xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
    android:layout_height="wrap_content"


    android:id="@+id/ScrollView01"

    android:fillViewport="false">

    <LinearLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
        xmlns:tools="http://schemas.android.com/tools" android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="match_parent" android:paddingLeft="@dimen/activity_horizontal_margin"

        android:paddingTop="@dimen/activity_vertical_margin"
        android:paddingBottom="@dimen/activity_vertical_margin"
        android:background="@drawable/bg8"
        tools:context="com.example.sudhanshumishra.astrovision.Libra"
        android:orientation="vertical"
        >


        <LinearLayout
            android:layout_width="380dp"
            android:layout_height="1250dp"
            android:weightSum="1"
            android:orientation="vertical"
            >

            <TextView
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="110dp"
                android:text="LIBRA"
                android:textSize="55dp"
                android:textStyle="bold"
                android:textAlignment="center"
                />


            <ImageView
                android:layout_width="320dp"
                android:layout_height="250dp"
                android:background="@drawable/libra" />

            <HorizontalScrollView
                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content">
                <TextView
                    android:layout_width="350dp"
                    android:layout_height="500dp"
                    android:layout_marginTop="15dp"
                    android:textColor="#F4F6F7"
                    android:text="Strength:\n
- Diplomatic\n
- Graceful\n
- Peaceful\n
- Idealistic\n
- Hospitable\n\n

Weakness:\n
- Superficial\n
- Vain\n
- Indecisive\nn
- Unreliable\n\n


Libras like to be around other people, they are \n
all about partnerships and groups. They are happiest \n
when other people are around and when other people are \n
doing their work. They are lazy but like posh surrounding \n
and nice decor. These two extremes could strike a balance \n
and the Libra living on his own could either have a very \n
messy place or a very intricately decorated place. They can \n
be independent, they have the intelligence and the full \n
capability within but would a Libra rather co-exist/depend \n
on others\n
"    />
            </HorizontalScrollView>
            <TextView
                android:layout_width="350dp"
                android:layout_height="60dp"
                android:id="@+id/tv_luck"
                android:textColor="#F4F6F7"
                />

            <EditText
                android:layout_width="320dp"
                android:layout_height="150dp"
                android:background="#FAD7A0"
                android:textColorHint="#A569BD"
                android:id="@id/edt_msg"
                />

            <Button
                android:layout_width="90dp"
                android:layout_height="60dp"
                android:layout_marginLeft="140dp"
                android:text="call"
                android:onClick="callme"
                />
            <Button
                android:layout_width="90dp"
                android:layout_height="60dp"
                android:layout_marginLeft="140dp"
                android:text="sms"
                android:onClick="send"
                />
        </LinearLayout>

        <LinearLayout
            android:layout_width="350dp"
            android:layout_height="60dp"
            android:layout_marginTop="30dp"
            >

            <Button
                android:layout_width="120dp"
                android:layout_height="60dp"
                android:text="Sign Out"
                android:textStyle="bold"
                android:textSize="10dp"
                android:layout_marginLeft="120dp"
                android:onClick="signout"
                />
        </LinearLayout>

    </LinearLayout>


</ScrollView>
